extends layout

block content
  h1(class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8") About Us
  
  .about-content(class="space-y-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white")
    div(class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm")
      h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3") Welcome to Our Platform
      p(class="mb-3") Welcome to our event registration platform. We help connect people with amazing events and experiences.
      p Our platform makes it easy to discover, register, and manage your participation in various events.
    
    div(class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm")
      h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3") Our Mission
      p(class="mb-3") To make event registration simple, efficient, and accessible for everyone.
      p Our platform is built with both event organizers and attendees in mind, ensuring a smooth experience for everyone involved.
    
    div(class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm")
      h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3") What We Offer
      ul(class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1")
        li Easy event registration process
        li Secure data handling
        li User-friendly interface
        li Real-time updates
        li Responsive customer support
    
    div(class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm")
      h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3") Contact Us
      p(class="mb-3") If you have any questions, feel free to reach out:
      ul(class="space-y-1")
        li Email: contact@example.com
        li Phone: (555) 123-4567
        li Address: 123 Event Street, City, Country 